(39, '3', 'Bài 1, 2, 3, 4 Trang 41, 42 Sgk Toán 2', '<p><strong>B&agrave;i 1. Đọc, viết:</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8080/thumb_522x219/giai-bai-1-2-3-4-trang-41-42-sgk-toan-2_1_1515118949.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải:</strong></p>\r\n<p>H&igrave;nh thứ hai:</p>\r\n<p>Đọc: Mười l&iacute;t</p>\r\n<p>Viết: 10l</p>\r\n<p>H&igrave;nh thứ ba:</p>\r\n<p>Đọc: Hai l&iacute;t</p>\r\n<p>Viết: 2l.</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i 2. T&iacute;nh (theo mẫu ):</strong></p>\r\n<p>a) &nbsp;9l + 8l = 17l &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;15l + 5l = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2l + 2l + 6l =</p>\r\n<p>b) 17l - 6l = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 18l - 5l = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;28l - 4l - 2l =</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p>a) 9l + 8l = 17l &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 15l + 5l = 20l &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2l + 2l + 6l = 10l</p>\r\n<p>b) 17l - 6l = 11l &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;18l - 5l = 13l &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 28l - 4l - 2l = 22l</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i 3. C&ograve;n bao nhi&ecirc;u l&iacute;t?</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8080/thumb_259x250/giai-bai-1-2-3-4-trang-41-42-sgk-toan-2_2_1515118949.jpg\" alt=\"\"></strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8080/thumb_489x227/giai-bai-1-2-3-4-trang-41-42-sgk-toan-2_3_1515118949.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p>b) 10l - 2l &nbsp;= 8l</p>\r\n<p>c) 20l - 10l = 10l.</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i 4.</strong>&nbsp;Lần đầu cửa h&agrave;ng b&aacute;n được 12l nước mắm, lần sau b&aacute;n được 15l nước mắm. Hỏi cả hai lần b&aacute;n được bao nhi&ecirc;u l&iacute;t nước mắm?</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p>Số l&iacute;t nước mắm cả hai lần cửa h&agrave;ng b&aacute;n được l&agrave;</p>\r\n<p>12 + 15 = 27 (l)</p>\r\n<p>Đ&aacute;p số: 27 l&iacute;t.</p>', '41', 'bai-1-2-3-4-trang-41-42-sgk-toan-2', '2022-07-07 21:10:13', '2022-07-07 21:10:13'),
(40, '3', 'Bài 1, 2, 3, 4 Trang 43 Sgk Toán 2', '<p><strong>B&agrave;i 1. T&iacute;nh:</strong></p>\r\n<p>2l + 1l = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 15l - 5l = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3l + 2l - 1l =&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>16l + 5l = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;35l - 12l = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 16l - 4l + 15l =</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p>2l + 1l = 3l &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 15l - 5l = 10l &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3l + 2l - 1l = 4l</p>\r\n<p>16l + 5l = 21l &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 35l - 12l = 23l &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;16l - 4l + 15l = 27l.</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i 2. Số?</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8080/thumb_364x147/giai-bai-1-2-3-4-trang-43-sgk-toan-2_1_1515119040.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p>a) 6l; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;b) 8l; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;c) 30l.</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i 3</strong>. Th&ugrave;ng thứ nhất c&oacute; 16l dầu, th&ugrave;ng thứ hai c&oacute; &iacute;t hơn th&ugrave;ng thứ nhất 2l dầu. Hỏi th&ugrave;ng thứ hai c&oacute; bao nhi&ecirc;u l&iacute;t dầu?</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p>Số l&iacute;t dầu th&ugrave;ng thứ hai c&oacute; l&agrave;:</p>\r\n<p>16 - 2 = 14 (l)</p>\r\n<p>Đ&aacute;p số: 14l.</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i 4.</strong>&nbsp;Thực h&agrave;nh: Đổ 1l nước từ chai 1l sang c&aacute;c cốc như nhau.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8080/thumb_218x176/giai-bai-1-2-3-4-trang-43-sgk-toan-2_2_1515119040.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>', '43', 'bai-1-2-3-4-trang-43-sgk-toan-2', '2022-07-07 21:10:33', '2022-07-07 21:10:33'),
(41, '3', 'Bài 1, 2, 3, 4, 5 Trang 44 Sgk Toán 2', '<p><strong>B&agrave;i 1. T&iacute;nh:</strong></p>\r\n<p>5 + 6 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;16 + 5 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 40 + 5 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4 + 16 =</p>\r\n<p>8 + 7 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;27 + 8 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 30 + 6 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3 + 47 =</p>\r\n<p>9 + 4 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;44 + 9 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 7 + 20 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 5 + 35 =</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p>5 + 6 = 11 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 16 + 5 = 21 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;40 + 5 = 45 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4 + 16 = 20</p>\r\n<p>8 + 7 = 15 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 27 + 8 = 35 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;30 + 6 = 36 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3 + 47 = 50</p>\r\n<p>9 + 4 = 13 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 44 + 9 = 53 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;7 + 20 = 27 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;5 + 35 = 40</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i 2. Số?</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8080/thumb_274x109/giai-bai-1-2-3-4-5-trang-44-sgk-toan-2_1_1515119102.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p>Hướng dẫn: H&igrave;nh a. 45kg; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; H&igrave;nh b. 45kg</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i 3. Viết số th&iacute;ch hợp v&agrave;o &ocirc; trống:</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8080/thumb_341x75/giai-bai-1-2-3-4-5-trang-44-sgk-toan-2_2_1515119102.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p>Hướng dẫn: Điền kết quả từ tr&aacute;i sang phải l&agrave;: 51, 93, 92, 63, 80.</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i 4. Giải b&agrave;i to&aacute;n theo t&oacute;m tắt sau:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Lần b&aacute;n đầu: 45kg gạo</p>\r\n<p>Lần b&aacute;n sau: 38kg gạo</p>\r\n<p>Cả hai lần b&aacute;n: ... kg gạo?</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p>Số kg cả hai lần b&aacute;n l&agrave;</p>\r\n<p>45 + 38 = 83 (kg)</p>\r\n<p>Đ&aacute;p số: 83 kg gạo.</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i 5. Khoanh v&agrave;o chữ đặt trước c&acirc;u trả lời đ&uacute;ng:</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8080/thumb_204x133/giai-bai-1-2-3-4-5-trang-44-sgk-toan-2_3_1515119102.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p>T&uacute;i gạo c&acirc;n nặng mấy kg?</p>\r\n<p>A. 1kg</p>\r\n<p>B. 2kg</p>\r\n<p>C. 3kg</p>\r\n<p>D. 4kg</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p>Khoanh v&agrave;o D.</p>', '44', 'bai-1-2-3-4-5-trang-44-sgk-toan-2', '2022-07-07 21:45:47', '2022-07-07 21:45:47'),
(42, '5', 'Bài 1, 2, 3 Trang 45 Sgk Toán 2', '<p><strong>B&agrave;i 1. T&igrave;m x (theo mẫu ):</strong></p>\r\n<p>a) x + 3 = 9 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;b) x + 5 = 10 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;e) 4 + x = 14</p>\r\n<p>x &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = 9 - 3 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;c) x + 2 = 8 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;g) 3 + x = 10</p>\r\n<p>x &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = 6 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;d) x + 8 = 19</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p>b) x + 5 = 10 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; e) 4 + x = 14</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; x &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = 10 - 5 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; x = 14 - 4</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; x &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = 5 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;x = 10</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>c) x + 2 = 8 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;g) 3 + x = 10</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;x &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= 8 - 2 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;x = 10 - 3</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;x &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= 6 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;x = 7</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>d) x + 8 = 19</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; x &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = 19 -8&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; x &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = 11</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i 2. Viết số th&iacute;ch hợp v&agrave;o &ocirc; trống:</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8080/thumb_377x105/giai-bai-1-2-3-trang-45-sgk-toan-2_1_1515119179.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p><strong>Hướng dẫn:</strong>&nbsp;Điền c&aacute;c số theo cột t&iacute;nh từ tr&aacute;i sang phải l&agrave;: 18, 1,10, 0, 21, 22.</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i 3.</strong>&nbsp;Một lớp học c&oacute; 35 học sinh, trong đ&oacute; c&oacute; 20 học sinh trai. Hỏi lớp đ&oacute; c&oacute; bao nhi&ecirc;u học sinh g&aacute;i?</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p>Số học sinh g&aacute;i của lớp l&agrave;:</p>\r\n<p>35 - 20 = 15 ( học sinh )</p>\r\n<p>Đ&aacute;p số: 15 học sinh.</p>', '45', 'bai-1-2-3-trang-45-sgk-toan-2', '2022-07-07 21:46:47', '2022-07-07 21:46:47'),
(43, '5', 'Bài 1, 2, 3, 4, 5 Trang 46 Sgk Toán 2', '<p><strong>B&agrave;i 1. T&igrave;m x:</strong></p>\r\n<p>a) x + 8 = 10; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; b) x + 7 = 10; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;c) 30 + x = 58.</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p>a) x + 8 = 10; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; b) x + 7 = 10; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;c) 30 + x = 58</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; x = 10 - 8 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; x = 10 - 7 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; x = 58 - 30</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; x = 2; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; x = 3 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;x = 28</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i 2. T&iacute;nh nhẩm:&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>9 + 1 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;8 + 2 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3 + 7 =&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>10 - 9 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10 - 8 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;10 - 3 =&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>10 - 1 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10 - 2 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;10 - 7 =</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p>9 + 1 = 10 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 8 + 2 = 10 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3 + 7 = 10</p>\r\n<p>10 - 9 = 1 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10 - 8 = 2 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10 - 3 = 7&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>10 - 1 = 9 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10 - 2 = 8 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10 - 7 = 3</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i 3. T&iacute;nh:&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>10 - 1 - 2 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10 - 3 - 4 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;19 - 3 - 5 =</p>\r\n<p>10 - 3 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;10 - 7 = &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 19- 8 =&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p>10 - 1 - 2 = 7 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;10 - 3 - 4 = 3 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 19 - 3 - 5 = 11</p>\r\n<p>10 - 3 = 7 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10 - 7 = 3 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;19 - 8 = 11</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i 4</strong>&nbsp;. Vừa cam vừa qu&yacute;t c&oacute; 45 quả, trong đ&oacute; c&oacute; 25 quả cam. Hỏi c&oacute; bao nhi&ecirc;u quả qu&yacute;t?</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p>Số quả qu&yacute;t l&agrave;:</p>\r\n<p>45 - 25 = 20 ( quả )</p>\r\n<p>Đ&aacute;p số: 20 quả qu&yacute;t.</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i 5. Khoanh v&agrave;o chữ đặt trước kết quả đ&uacute;ng:</strong></p>\r\n<p>T&igrave;m x, biết: x + 5 = 5&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>A. x = 5</p>\r\n<p>B. x = 10</p>\r\n<p>C. x = 0</p>\r\n<p>Khoanh đ&aacute;p &aacute;n C.</p>', '46', 'bai-1-2-3-4-5-trang-46-sgk-toan-2', '2022-07-07 21:47:21', '2022-07-07 21:47:21'),
(44, '5', 'Bài 1, 2, 3 Trang 47 Sgk Toán 2', '<p><strong>B&agrave;i 1. T&iacute;nh:</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8080/thumb_403x56/giai-bai-1-2-3-trang-47-sgk-toan-2_1_1515119338.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8080/thumb_355x64/giai-bai-1-2-3-trang-47-sgk-toan-2_2_1515119338.jpg\" alt=\"\"></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i 2. T&igrave;m x:&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>a) x + 9 = 30; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;b) 5 + x = 20; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;c) x + 19 = &nbsp;60</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p>a) x + 9 = 30; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; b) 5 + x = 20; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;c) x + 19 = 60</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; x &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = 30 - 9 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;x = 20 - 5 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; x &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= 60 - 19</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; x &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = 21. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;x = 15 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; x &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = 41</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i 3</strong>. C&oacute; 2 chục que t&iacute;nh, bớt đi 5 que t&iacute;nh. hỏi c&ograve;n lại bao nhi&ecirc;u que t&iacute;nh?</p>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i giải</strong></p>\r\n<p>Số que t&iacute;nh c&ograve;n lại l&agrave;:</p>\r\n<p>20 - 5 = 15 (que t&iacute;nh )</p>\r\n<p>Đ&aacute;p số: 15 que t&iacute;nh.</p>', '47', 'bai-1-2-3-trang-47-sgk-toan-2', '2022-07-07 21:47:37', '2022-07-07 21:47:37');
